# sprint-implementation (frontend)

MUST:
- TDD: failing mapper/hook test before production code
- test subject named `sut`
- test name: `should {outcome} when {condition}` (Vitest it(...))
- English-only: branches, commits, identifiers, test names
- flow: Service(DTO) → Mapper → Domain Model → Component
- domain models in UI from `src/features/domain/models/` only
- `parseDateOnly()` for API `YYYY-MM-DD` strings
- branch: `{type}/{english-kebab-slug}` from `main`

NEVER:
- code comments in production or test code
- import `src/types/api/` in UI components
- `any`, `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`, `eval`
- non-English branch/commit/identifier names
- edit existing test before classifying failure

TEST_BROKEN:
- IF existing test fails → fix implementation first
- ONLY update test if requirement changed, test was wrong, or internal refactor without contract change

